Dear %str1%,
I hope all is well with you. Big update from the Well Kingdom of Winslow: I've recently amassed a new court. Before you ask, yes, they are rats. They're not the most talkative bunch, but they don't talk back to their regent, and that's what counts. That garden never worked out, so I've moved my efforts over to armoring. The Kingdom of Winslow endures. 

Lord Blaine, Prince of Winslow

New Loamhurst has endured much since its founding, but nothing on the scale of the war that landed on our doorstep. With your help and the continued support of the Seraph, however, we will be victorious. No matter what happens to us, we will always replant and rebuild. Thank you for all that you've done. 

—Elder Vern
